MODIFICATIONS FROM UPSTREAM (chartdb/chartdb):

This is a modified version of ChartDB, originally created by the ChartDB
contributors and licensed under AGPL-3.0.

Summary of modifications (2025–2026):
- Rebranded from ChartDB to BoringDB
- Added AI-powered schema generation via Cloudflare Workers AI
- Added SQL auto-detection fallback (detects SQL output and routes through
  the existing SQL import pipeline instead of requiring DBML)
- Added robust DBML syntax fixer (fixDBMLSyntax) for LLM output normalization
- Added Cloudflare Workers deployment with AI proxy and stream normalization
- Added Drizzle ORM schema export (deterministic code generation for
  PostgreSQL, MySQL, and SQLite via drizzle-orm/pg-core, mysql-core, sqlite-core)
- Added 6 AI-focused schema templates (RAG Pipeline, AI Gateway, Prompt
  Management, Evals Platform, Multi-Agent Orchestration, MCP Server Registry)
- Added template generator CLI (scripts/generate-template.ts)
- Removed third-party analytics (Fathom)
- Removed external social links and GitHub star prompts
- PNG logo and branding replacement

